'''Paul Huston''' was the senior digital matte artist on the [[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition|''Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition'']] release. Huston's work on the re-release of ''Star Wars'' began in [[1994]] and included new [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] scenes as well as shots of [[Ben Kenobi's hut]].

